javax.script
Class ScriptEngineManager

java.lang.Object
  javax.script.ScriptEngineManager

public class ScriptEngineManager
extends java.lang.Object

ScriptEngineManager implements a discovery and instantiation mechanisams for ScriptEngine class. It also contains a collection of key-value pairs which storing state shared by all engines created by manager. Nandika Jayawardana Sanka Samaranayake
